OL,3,CStars hit red carpet for premiere of
OL,4,CPeaky Blinders: The Immortal Man
OL,6,FCillian Murphy and Rebecca Ferguson,
OL,7,Fwho star in the film both spoke ITV
OL,8,FNews Central ahead of the premiere in
OL,9,FBirmingham
OL,11,FPeaky Blinders creator Steven Knight
OL,12,Fhas said shooting will start soon on
OL,13,Fthe "brilliant" follow-up series to
OL,14,FThe Immortal Man feature film.
OL,16,FSpeaking on the red carpet at the
OL,17,Fworld premiere of the film in
OL,18,FBirmingham, Knight said it had been a
OL,19,F"very, very happy" experience to make
OL,20,FThe Immortal Man in his home city.
OL,26,@uD@EOUuD@OO]{D@AOU{D@RO]
