PN,37602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1772582588
OL,3,CStars hit red carpet for premiere of
OL,4,CPeaky Blinders: The Immortal Man
OL,6,FThe much-awaited feature film, which
OL,7,Flaunches in select cinemas on Friday
OL,8,Fand on Netflix from March 20, is set
OL,9,Fin Birmingham in 1940 and sees Cillian
OL,10,FMurphy reprise his role as Tommy
OL,11,FShelby in a film written by Knight and
OL,12,Fdirected by Tom Harper.
OL,14,FAsked to describe the experience of
OL,15,Fmaking film in Birmingham, with
OL,16,Fprevious series often shot in northern
OL,17,FEngland, Knight said: "Before, we shot
OL,18,Fa lot of it in the north but I sort of
OL,19,Finsisted that this one we do here.
OL,26,@yD@WOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1772582588
OL,3,CStars hit red carpet for premiere of
OL,4,CPeaky Blinders: The Immortal Man
OL,6,F"And the production team were
OL,7,Fabsolutely astonished by what we got
OL,8,Fhere, what we got in terms of
OL,9,Flocations, of how the city looks, and
OL,10,Fthe way they were welcomed.
OL,12,F"So it was a very, very happy
OL,13,Fexperience to shoot it here."
OL,15,FAsked what lay ahead in terms of the
OL,16,FPeaky Blinders series, Knight
OL,17,Fresponded: "I can't tell you a lot
OL,18,Fbecause I'm not allowed to. But it's
OL,19,Fafter the war and it's brilliant.
OL,21,F"We start shooting very soon."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUuD@]O]yD@LOU}D@AOU}D@^O]
