PN,37604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1772582588
OL,3,CStars hit red carpet for premiere of
OL,4,CPeaky Blinders: The Immortal Man
OL,6,FThe Immortal Man sees Duke Shelby,
OL,7,Fplayed by Barry Keoghan, and a new
OL,8,Fgeneration of Peaky Blinders drawn
OL,9,Finto a Nazi plot that puts the future
OL,10,Fof the family at stake as Britain and
OL,11,Fthe rest of Europe battle Hitler's war
OL,12,Fmachine.
OL,14,FAlso speaking at the film launch, amid
OL,15,Fan extensive array of props in
OL,16,FBirmingham's Centenary Square, Murphy
OL,17,Fsaid of The Immortal Man: "I think if
OL,18,Fyou write great parts, you get great
OL,19,Factors."
OL,26,@yD@[OU{D@HO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/10
