FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1772582588
OL,3,CStars hit red carpet for premiere of
OL,4,CPeaky Blinders: The Immortal Man
OL,6,FAsked how the character of Tommy
OL,7,FShelby had developed from shortly
OL,8,Fafter the First World War to 1940,
OL,9,FMurphy told the Press Association: "Oh
OL,10,Fmy God, I don't know if I can give you
OL,11,Fthat in a soundbite. You'd need to
OL,12,Fwatch the 36 hours of TV. It's kind of
OL,13,Fvery, very complex, you know."
OL,15,FHe added: "I'm immensely proud of the
OL,16,Fwork, I'm immensely proud of the show,
OL,17,FI'm immensely proud of the fans."
OL,19,FMurphy said of acting and filming in
OL,20,FBirmingham: "Loved it, it was amazing."
OL,26,@qD@dOUuD@^O]wD@KOUyD@aO]|D@MOU|D@gO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/10
