PN,37606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1772582588
OL,3,CStars hit red carpet for premiere of
OL,4,CPeaky Blinders: The Immortal Man
OL,6,FKnight, who earlier on Monday unveiled
OL,7,Fa West Midlands Metro tram named in
OL,8,Fhis honour, said: "Birmingham is one
OL,9,Fof the stars of the film. It's a great
OL,10,Fstory. It's very entertaining, and I
OL,11,Fam told that the reaction... there's a
OL,12,Flot of emotion around it.
OL,14,F"There's a lot of people end the thing
OL,15,Fin tears, which is great because
OL,16,Fthat's what we wanted. So, yeah, I
OL,17,Fthink it's a very powerful piece, and
OL,18,FI'm really proud of it."
OL,26,@pD@SOUvD@AOUzD@XO]
