OL,3,CStars hit red carpet for premiere of
OL,4,CPeaky Blinders: The Immortal Man
OL,6,FReservoir Dogs actor Tim Roth and co-
OL,7,Fstar Rebecca Ferguson also spoke on
OL,8,Fthe red carpet ahead of the screening.
OL,10,FFerguson, who takes on the role of
OL,11,FKaulo in the film, said working with
OL,12,FKnight and Harper had been
OL,13,F"incredible" and likened it to
OL,14,F"sitting in a pub with some mates and
OL,15,Fplaying some cards and having some
OL,16,Fpints".
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@LO]vD@AOUxD@FO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1772582588
OL,3,CStars hit red carpet for premiere of
OL,4,CPeaky Blinders: The Immortal Man
OL,6,F"It's safe, and I think when you have
OL,7,Fa safe set you are free to explore and
OL,8,Fyou are free to have fun, and to not
OL,9,Fthink about making a fool of
OL,10,Fyourself," she said.
OL,12,FRoth, who plays Beckett, said he had
OL,13,Fchosen not to watch previous series of
OL,14,FPeaky Blinders before portraying his
OL,15,Fcharacter, opting to hold off and come
OL,16,Fto his role "completely fresh".
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@JO]xD@MOUxD@^O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
