OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1772582588
OL,3,CStars hit red carpet for premiere of
OL,4,CPeaky Blinders: The Immortal Man
OL,6,FAsked if he had sought Murphy's advice
OL,7,Fbefore making the decision, Roth
OL,8,Fanswered: "No. I was a bit nervous
OL,9,Fabout telling him to be honest, but he
OL,10,Flaughed, which is typical Cillian."
OL,12,FHarper said of making the movie on the
OL,13,Fstreets of Birmingham: "It was
OL,14,Factually, honestly, really wonderful.
OL,16,F"It's hard to explain, but when you're
OL,17,Fon the streets of Digbeth or Small
OL,18,FHeath ` that is the place where the
OL,19,Fmyth of the Peaky Blinders was born.
OL,26,@pD@KOUrD@cO]uD@XOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1772582588
OL,3,CStars hit red carpet for premiere of
OL,4,CPeaky Blinders: The Immortal Man
OL,6,F"Sometimes, if you just close your
OL,7,Feyes for a minute you can almost slip
OL,8,Fback in time and feel what it must
OL,9,Fhave been like for those characters,
OL,10,Fliving in that time, and I think that
OL,11,Fcan't help but seep into the
OL,12,Ffilmmaking. And then, hopefully, when
OL,13,Fthe audience watches the film, they'll
OL,14,Ffeel that too."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@OO]
